title: Two Sides to Every Date: The Shirtless Selfie
description: Tyler is wondering what went wrong with Lisa, a woman he's gone on a couple dates with and now she hasn't been responding to his texts.  Lisa agreed to be on to tell what went wrong but then she hung up so Jenny had to do some digging and was able to reveal what happened.
